<abstract>
<title
>Zusammenfassung</title>
<para
> Die <application
>Anleitung zum Bibelstudium</application
> ist ein Handbuch zum Studieren der Bibel. </para>
<para
>It is the hope of the &bibletime; team that this HowTo will provoke the readers to study the scriptures to see what they say. This particular study guide has been chosen as it takes care not to advocate any particular denominational doctrine. We expect you to read and study the scriptures to understand what they say. If you start with the attitude that you want to have the Lord sow his word in your heart He will not disappoint you.</para>
